En este tutorial se puede aprender a '''comprar''' (comprar o construir), '''vender''' (eliminar) y '''reformar''' las aeronaves.

==Comprar aeronaves==
Pasos para comprar una aeronave:
* Construya un [[es/Manual/Construir aeropuertos|aeropuerto]].
* Haga clic en el hangar situado en el aeropuerto para abrir la ventana Hangar de aeronaves.
[[File:es/Manual/Step1aircraft.png|none|thumb|450px|Ventana Hangar de aeronaves]]

{{es/Pendiente de traducci√≥n}}

* Click on the New Aircraft button located on the lower left-side of the Aircraft Hangar window. This will bring up the New Aircraft window.

*Browse the list of available aircraft, select one, and press the Build Aircraft button.  A window will appear showing the aircraft in the Hangar. 
[[File:en/Manual/Step3aircraft.png|none|frame|Selecting an aircraft]]

*If you want to carry something else than passengers and mail, you need to [[en/Manual/Refit]] the aircraft.  While it is standing in the hangar, press the "refit" button in the Aircraft window.
[[File:en/Manual/Step4aircraft.png|none|frame|The aircraft window for your new aircraft!]]